{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"549a6e5f4d","title":"卜算子·停艾地同志","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ea8c68e524","index":0,"year":1965,"month":12,"day":null,"articleId":"549a6e5f4d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji48","name":"毛泽东全集第48卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/48-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji48":{"comments":[{"id":"9637e59717","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"549a6e5f4d","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"艾地（1923-1965），印度尼西亚共产党主要领导人，国际共产主义运动著名活动家。"},{"id":"0b3c4efa41","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"549a6e5f4d","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"疏枝，指梅花。梅花开放时有花无叶，开花后始生叶，故其枝条稀疏。立寒窗，指梅花在冬末早春时开放，天气寒冷，人们常栽于窗前庭院中，以供观赏。"},{"id":"1cb335bccf","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"549a6e5f4d","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"笑，欢笑。形容花儿绽开，似人显露笑容。14]反，反而。调，调谢。残，残缺，坏。调残，花木枯菱，调谢。"},{"id":"c6bf307e53","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"549a6e5f4d","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"固，固然，本来。不堪，不能忍受，表示程度之深。残固不堪残，梅花已经洞零得非常厉害了。"},{"id":"1a8ce79f42","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"549a6e5f4d","index":5,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"蓄芳待来年，意思是说梅花每年都有开放的时候，现在虽然调谢了，但是明年还会再开放，比喻只要不断地积聚力量，革命运动终会重新掘起。"}],"contents":[{"id":"e92589c44f","type":"title","text":"下算子.恒艾地同志","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"549a6e5f4d"},{"id":"9637e59717","type":"paragraph","text":"疏枝立寒窗以，笑以在百花前。奈何笑容难为久，春来反调残。残固不堪残以，何须自寻烦。花落自有花开日，","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"549a6e5f4d"},{"id":"0b3c4efa41","type":"subtitle","text":"蓄芳待来年队","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"549a6e5f4d"}],"page":{"id":"1ddb16cc52","publicationId":"ma